body.name: Hasuit Black Dresser for Bedroom with LED Lights and Charging Station, 51.2" Long Dresser Chest of Drawers with Large Drawers and Open Space, Modern 6 Drawer Dresser for Bedroom, Living Room, Entryway
features: 【Enough Storage Space】LED black dresser with 6 large capacity drawers allows you to store personal items in categories, including clothing, books, cosmetics toys, etc. The 51.2" spacious desktop can double as a dresser TV stand or be used to place photos, lamps, green plants, and other items. Two open storage spaces on the top floors ensure everything you need is within easy reach. The chest of drawers can function in any corner of your bedroom, closet or living room to keep your room clean and tidy.

【Dresser with RGB LED Lights】LED lights color adds a modern and stylish flair. It looks prettier in the dark and adds a unique vibe to your bedroom. It can be controlled by button control or APP. It has more than 60,000 colors to choose from, the brightness can be adjusted, and many other modes are waiting for you to explore: custom style mode, music mode, mic mode, and timing function.

【Chest of Drawers with Charging Station】LED Dresser is equipped with 2 standard plug outlets and 2 USB ports, as well as a 6.56-foot-long power cord. Enables you to charge mobile devices such as smartphones, tablets, or smartwatches, and other appliances at any time. The red power button and easy control switch to keep you safe. That makes things more convenient for you if you don't have enough outlets in your room.

【Quality Assurance】The black chest of drawers is made of sturdy engineering wood. The high-quality metal slide rail makes it easy to pull the drawer. A thick back plate and stable base design ensure the stability of the drawer dresser and have a strong bearing capacity. Waterproof and scratch resistant, easy to clean, and equipped with a safe anti-fall device to protect your family.

【Modern Practical Minimalist】Modern LED bedroom black dresser features a simple design. Chest of drawers can easily fit into any décor style, saving space while adding a touch of sophistication to your home decor. Use it alone or in combination with other Hasuit chests of drawers.

【Let Us Know】Hasuit 6 drawer dresser has clear Installation steps, and all parts are individually packed and marked. If you have any problems with assembly and instructions, please contact our store's support team first and we’ll give you a solution. Thank you for your support and trust！
